snippet.title: Worms W.M.D: All-Stars Preorder Pack! (Multi-platform)
snippet.description:
The Worms are getting ready for battle and have enlisted the help from a few friends... 

Joining the ruckus we have an army of guest stars bringing with them weapons, customization, campaign levels and even a vehicle :

- Rocket League
- Orcs Must Die Unchained
- Unturned
- Goat Simulator
- PAYDAY 2
- The Escapists
- Yooka-Laylee
- Worms
- Saints Row IV
- Broforce

Xbox One Exclusive Content Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TN6HFUjV7s8
Steam Exclusive Content Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kb0vMfcE9-o

Follow Worms on Twitter: http://bit.ly/FollowWorms

Team17, founded in 1990, are a fully independent Video Game Developer and Games Label, responsible for the Worms™ series, Beyond Eyes, Sheltered and many more. Ensure you never miss out on our latest videos by subscribing to us now: bit.ly/SubTeam17
